{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"191544-dhobighatta-diwas","title":"धोबिघट्टा दिवस","description":"आजुक दिन मैरीक प्रिय समय थिक - कपड़ा धोबाक समय। मैरीक पड़ोसियासभसँ भेंट कऽ लिअ कारणजे ओ लोकनि कपडा धो रहल छथि आ निकलि जेताह फेर नव दिन काज शुरू करऽ लेल।","language":"Maithili","langCode":"mai","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Babujeek Library"],"illustrators":["Shambhavi Singh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/191544-dhobighatta-diwas"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55464/size3/56deae620a87cdf1061749233170a37b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55464/size6/56deae620a87cdf1061749233170a37b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55466/size6/8858892456500011a690a65c50e80053.jpg","text":"हमर नाम मैरी थिक।\nहम एतऽ रहैत छी।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55471/size6/b93a837a75194681cfe100ca77786ddf.jpg","text":"3/25","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55469/size6/a265e50da8c421147020ee8a71886814.jpg","text":"आइ नव दिन अछि।\nतात्पर्य ई जे ई समय थिक कपड़ा धोऽबाक।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55474/size6/9a20f51059d022fc0f3e0ecc40a0b0e3.jpg","text":"5/25","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55472/size6/ca8ed41e2759fc1de2259383d8366bd8.jpg","text":"हर एक केर बाहु बुलबुलासँ झपायल अछि।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55496/size6/877b51a498919ca376d22dfb93adec02.jpg","text":"7/25","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/72926/size6/1660a3a8e98116f3896f4910a847abfe.jpg","text":"फेनिल गड़हइ गलीकेँ इन्द्रधनुष बना देलक अछि।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55480/size6/a5ba6375c727d9a44c0b14a8e0a05d7d.jpg","text":"9/25","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55475/size6/59498b7d4cec83fd47ce5162ca066dd8.jpg","text":"ग्रेस काकी अपन वर्दी धोइ छथि।\nकाल्हि पहिरकऽ चिकित्सालयमे रोगीकेँ देखऽ जेतीह।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55477/size6/cf6446949abc572e1c766b89d296442d.jpg","text":"11/25","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55481/size6/f1f4b3b586278039e8b9242476131b30.jpg","text":"जौना मासी अपन गाममे दाइक बुनल कम्बलकेँ टाँगैत छथि।\nसूतक रंग जौना मौसीक घरक रंग सन अछि।","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55479/size6/e18e0a4fd268366175e526ec069dd9dd.jpg","text":"13/25","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55485/size6/8f99f798c737e3d69943e060fb2d4cd5.jpg","text":"फातिमा आपाक डोरि दुपट्टासँ भरल अछि।\nजखन ओकरा ओ अपन माथ पर बन्हतीह, तऽ गमकि उठत।","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55484/size6/7ced14eed8f87948586fe0fa28a6ce63.jpg","text":"15/25","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55483/size6/4a61f4afe41602b5d852d1da6cda37d4.jpg","text":"जाकिर चाचाक ऑटोवला वर्दी घरक बाहर टाँगल अछि।\nओ अपन स्वच्छ कमीजमे टूटल बटम टाँकैत छथि।","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55482/size6/6a210915945479273765f1ba71cb55b5.jpg","text":"17/25","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55487/size6/8359bd8f0db9456f8294bd4beca3cf34.jpg","text":"गीता काकीक घरमे टाँगल सूती साड़ी हवामे लहरा रहल अछि।\nपक्षीक फड़फड़ैत पाँखि सदृश ध्वनि आबि रहल अछि।","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55486/size6/428de28f34f3c812625cab6405bcc487.jpg","text":"19/25","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55489/size6/c28b2e3d6272fbf5bc71707b3b5d2ea8.jpg","text":"जोसेफ चाचाक डोरि पर पतेबा पसरल  अछि।\nअपन पारीमे काज करऽ काल पतेबा हुनक तरबाकेँ गरम रखैत छनि।","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55488/size6/c59b35c86c3b60bdabbdffd20959d100.jpg","text":"21/25","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55491/size6/f124a44d585043eb81a0666167423fb2.jpg","text":"हम आर हमर भाइ डेविड अपन स्कूलक पोशाख धोइ छी।\nहम दूनू गोटे जेबी पर स्याही आ  छोड़ैब आ आस्तीन पर पथरखड़ीक लागल दाँगकेँ रगड़िकेँ छोड़बैत छी।","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55490/size6/6e79b79c307f46cd06bb69058a2d5936.jpg","text":"23/25","words":null},{"n":23,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55495/size6/a533e3bc98afefd051adae051db8fe7c.jpg","text":"काल्हि फेर कपड़ा गन्दा भऽ जैत। \nकिन्तु एखन सभ चकाचक अछि।","words":null},{"n":24,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55494/size6/87d83cd80708c34b2c406d2d63ace548.jpg","text":"25/25","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":24,"words":181}}